reviews.name: Skyline 5-Piece Daybed Set
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this set for a guest room/office. The fabric and construction are good quality. I saw this set on other sites for much more. Great value for the price.
reviews.title: Great looking daybed set

reviews.name: Skyline 5-Piece Daybed Set
reviews.reviewText: Purchased this along with a new daybed for a spare room and am very pleased with it. The picture doesn't due it justice. It actually looks better and has some teal coloring in it as well that you can't see in pic. Price was great for the set and it fits and looks great on the daybed.
reviews.title: Excellent value, great looking

reviews.name: Skyline 5-Piece Daybed Set
reviews.reviewText: Nicer than picture. Taupe and light turquoise in the biege circles. I've seen this from same manufacturer online for double the cost. Great value
reviews.title: Daybed cover

reviews.name: Skyline 5-Piece Daybed Set
reviews.reviewText:
I was a little surprised when I received this comforter set, because the colors were not what I expected. The skirt focused on the darker colors from the comforter.
Even though it does not look the same online as it does in real life, I was very pleased with the set. It was purchased for my spare bedroom, and it looks great!
The price was also reasonable.
reviews.title: Not what I expected...

reviews.name: Skyline 5-Piece Daybed Set
reviews.reviewText: I love the silky feel of all the fabrics. We have a golden retreiver dog and her hair blows right off the fabric. It all looks very expensive. I saw the same set for sale elsewhere for $50.00 more! The only disappointment was the bed skirt was not the color pictured. It came in the dark brown tones, not the cream tones as I was expecting. I wanted the cream because of the dog. But it all looks great. I would recommend the overall quality.
reviews.title: Great quality--colors are not what is pictured
